description: The assault on a man, 19, happened in Rectory Road, Sittingbourne, just after midnight, police say.
title: Woman arrested after teenager stabbed
title_page: Sittingbourne: Woman arrested after teenager stabbed in street - BBC News
maintext:
A woman has been arrested after a teenager was stabbed in a residential area of a Kent town.
The victim in his late teens, was assaulted near Rectory Road in Sittingbourne shortly after midnight, Kent Police said.
He was taken by air ambulance to a London hospital where he remains in a serious but stable condition.
A local woman, aged 19, was later arrested on suspicion of assault and taken into custody.
